No new user-controlled data is injected into HTML/JS without escaping (no CWE-79), no OS/command execution is added or modified (no CWE-77/78), no prototype properties are modified from untrusted input (no CWE-1321), and there is no embedded malicious logic (no CWE-506). The changes are internal library/build behavior and do not introduce the specified vulnerabilities.
